Package com.commander4j.messages

Class IncommingProcessOrder

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.messages.IncommingProcessOrder
public class IncommingProcessOrder
extends java.lang.Object
IncommingProcessOrder creates or updates records in the APP_PROCESS_ORDER table. Some verification is performed before the table is updated. If errors are found the insert/update does not occur and an error is written to the SYS_INTERFACE_LOG table with a description of the failure reason.
